{"tid":1387781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想問下大家覺得依條友似唔似葉虎?","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T08:37:17.000Z","uid":73381,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e9cb15fa9c4d6f83c5bc7973fd8e03c4ff89dbc4","tid":1387781,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"話說嗰晚用搜到武器架車嘅車牌查土地冊會見到其中有一個人叫做葉悅達<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JnVjapU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJnVjapU.png&h=fdc5272b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htwqRJO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhtwqRJO.jpg&h=f9e9d930&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而係葉悅達嘅FB fd搭fd咁搵 會搵到一個叫做Ip Yip嘅人 樣貌同葉虎有幾分相似<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZLWN3J4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZLWN3J4.png&h=ff0ae9df&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁依位Ip Yip嘅其中一位朋友叫做 Ip Yf  應該就係土地冊入面嗰個Ip Yuet Fat / Ip Yuk Fu ?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JhUoB4e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJhUoB4e.png&h=f9303fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ypFfuqB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FypFfuqB.jpg&h=504c96e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果證明到Ip Yip就係葉虎的話 係咪就代表可以確認葉虎同依單嘢有關係?"},{"pid":"acc10747732ad7a463de5431bea9d0bbadb7c3fa","tid":1387781,"uid":73381,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:08:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GVLGCXfZOWM/XT92bTvvAmI/AAAAAAAFtb8/iPcJVeu6ODkuEKT6nh8uofqY8TKZoPDggCKgBGAs/s400/sketch-1564439496885.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-GVLGCXfZOWM%2FXT92bTvvAmI%2FAAAAAAAFtb8%2FiPcJVeu6ODkuEKT6nh8uofqY8TKZoPDggCKgBGAs%2Fs400%2Fsketch-1564439496885.png&h=cb61ba27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8B